<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>政治 on 总有一些人先看到未来</title><link>/categories/%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB/</link><description>Recent content in 政治 on 总有一些人先看到未来</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 10 Feb 2024 23:39:16 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="/categories/%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB/rss.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>阿根廷米莱，回到了正确的方向上来了</title><link>/_drafts/%E9%98%BF%E6%A0%B9%E5%BB%B7%E7%B1%B3%E8%8E%B1%E5%9B%9E%E5%88%B0%E4%BA%86%E6%AD%A3%E7%A1%AE%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E5%90%91%E4%B8%8A%E6%9D%A5%E4%BA%86/</link><pubDate>Sat, 10 Feb 2024 23:39:16 +0000</pubDate><guid>/_drafts/%E9%98%BF%E6%A0%B9%E5%BB%B7%E7%B1%B3%E8%8E%B1%E5%9B%9E%E5%88%B0%E4%BA%86%E6%AD%A3%E7%A1%AE%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E5%90%91%E4%B8%8A%E6%9D%A5%E4%BA%86/</guid><description>&lt;p>阿根廷米莱 回到了正确的方向上来了&lt;/p>
&lt;p>米莱在国会进行了一个多小时的长篇演讲。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>演讲全文我整理放在另一个号上，可以关注阅读&lt;/p>
&lt;p>这次演讲，其实是米莱受到挫败后的一次努力。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>米莱在上任不到一个月，就推出了一个包含几百项改革的紧急改革法案，这个法案，不仅有各项改革，还要求议会给予他一个较长时间的紧急状态下、不需要议会给他授权以应对经济危机的改革权力。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>《心灵鸡汤》的本质及危害</title><link>/_drafts/%E5%BF%83%E7%81%B5%E9%B8%A1%E6%B1%A4%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%AC%E8%B4%A8%E5%8F%8A%E5%8D%B1%E5%AE%B3/</link><pubDate>Thu, 23 Dec 2021 23:39:16 +0000</pubDate><guid>/_drafts/%E5%BF%83%E7%81%B5%E9%B8%A1%E6%B1%A4%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%AC%E8%B4%A8%E5%8F%8A%E5%8D%B1%E5%AE%B3/</guid><description/></item><item><title>白领陨落，黑领崛起</title><link>/_drafts/%E7%99%BD%E9%A2%86%E9%99%A8%E8%90%BD%E9%BB%91%E9%A2%86%E5%B4%9B%E8%B5%B7/</link><pubDate>Thu, 23 Dec 2021 23:39:16 +0000</pubDate><guid>/_drafts/%E7%99%BD%E9%A2%86%E9%99%A8%E8%90%BD%E9%BB%91%E9%A2%86%E5%B4%9B%E8%B5%B7/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;strong>白领陨落，黑领崛起&lt;/strong>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>论传统汉字和现代文明的冲突</title><link>/_drafts/%E8%AE%BA%E4%BC%A0%E7%BB%9F%E6%B1%89%E5%AD%97%E5%92%8C%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E6%96%87%E6%98%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%86%B2%E7%AA%81/</link><pubDate>Thu, 23 Dec 2021 23:39:16 +0000</pubDate><guid>/_drafts/%E8%AE%BA%E4%BC%A0%E7%BB%9F%E6%B1%89%E5%AD%97%E5%92%8C%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E6%96%87%E6%98%8E%E7%9A%84%E5%86%B2%E7%AA%81/</guid><description/></item><item><title>美帝是怎样通过“大片”给我们洗脑的</title><link>/_drafts/%E7%BE%8E%E5%B8%9D%E6%98%AF%E6%80%8E%E6%A0%B7%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E5%A4%A7%E7%89%87%E7%BB%99%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E6%B4%97%E8%84%91%E7%9A%84/</link><pubDate>Thu, 23 Dec 2021 23:39:16 +0000</pubDate><guid>/_drafts/%E7%BE%8E%E5%B8%9D%E6%98%AF%E6%80%8E%E6%A0%B7%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E5%A4%A7%E7%89%87%E7%BB%99%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E6%B4%97%E8%84%91%E7%9A%84/</guid><description>&lt;p>美帝是怎样通过“大片”给我们洗脑的&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>浅析“被逼婚”的本质</title><link>/_drafts/%E6%B5%85%E6%9E%90%E8%A2%AB%E9%80%BC%E5%A9%9A%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%AC%E8%B4%A8%E5%92%8C%E6%84%9F%E6%81%A9%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2/</link><pubDate>Thu, 23 Dec 2021 23:39:16 +0000</pubDate><guid>/_drafts/%E6%B5%85%E6%9E%90%E8%A2%AB%E9%80%BC%E5%A9%9A%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%AC%E8%B4%A8%E5%92%8C%E6%84%9F%E6%81%A9%E6%95%99%E